page1.title: About Me
page1.content: I’m ForBo7: an approachable, adaptable, open-minded, curious individual who’s been to seventeen countries and lived in three. I’m a science and technology geek, space nerd, and currently dabble in AI. 3D computer graphics is my hobby and learning is my passion. .
